            <title>[LU-14037] lu_device_fini()) ASSERTION( atomic_read(&amp;d-&gt;ld_ref) == 0 )</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14037</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mntput() is not synchronous and schedules real work to another thread. thus osd_device_fini() doesn&apos;t wait for commit callbacks to complete, which in turn hold references to lu_device.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
